commit.message: 2.7.11a_Diploid_TrSAMfix. Behavior change: replaced --quantTranscriptomeBan option with --quantTranscriptomeSAMoutput option. New option: --quantTranscriptomeSAMoutput BanSingleEnd_ExtendSoftclip : prohibit single-end alignments, extend softclips, allow indels.
Issue #1909: Fixed a bug causing wrong sequence length in the UB SAM tag for --soloType CB_UMI_Complex.
2.7.10b_alpha_2023-07-19. Finalized --soloCBtype String option for arbitrary cell barcode strings without passlist.
Implemented  option for arbitrary cell barcode strings without passlist.
Added STARsolo BAM tag sF, which outputs the feature type and number of genes for each read.
2.7.10b_alpha_23-06-20: Fixed a GstrandBit issue for the on-the-fly insertion of extra genomic sequences.
2.7.10b_alpha_23-06-09: Issue #1871: Fixed a bug which occurs when --soloCellReadStats Standard --twopassMode Basic are used together.
Fixed haplotype tag (ha) for STARdiploid SAM/BAM output.
Fixed issues with 2-pass and WASP for diploid genome mapping.
Fixed primary flag for diploid transformation.
2.7.10b_alpha_230301: Issue #1763: Fixed a bug causing segnmentation fault in rare cases for 2-pass mapping.
2.7.10b_alpha_220111: Issue #1733: Fixed the issue with counting of intronicAS reads in STARsolo CellReads.stats output with --soloFeatures GeneFull_Ex50pAS option.
